{"id":624668,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/【真理部指令】关于港澳台等问题的正确提法和禁/","date":"2019-12-18T10:02:57Z","modified":"2019-12-18T10:24:51Z","title":"【真理部指令】关于港澳台等问题的正确提法和禁忌","content":"<p>CDT编者按：近日，一位匿名网友在网络上公布了某出版社<strong>内部编辑资料</strong>，涉及到大量的“审查禁忌”。据悉，这些资料是其出版社为执行有关部门具体<strong>审查“红线”</strong>要求所做的详细操作化指南（CDT注：也有可能是官方直接下发 因为与（1）有大量内容雷同 ）。</p>\n<p>这些文件涉及到“台湾的机构名称和职务称呼”、“党和国家领导人的提法和禁忌”、“重大提法和历史问题”、“民族和宗教问题”、“港澳台和国际组织的一些禁忌”、“地图问题”等多个方面。</p>\n<p>1.台湾的机构名称和职务称呼</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9h1S4UYAMJmZS.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624669\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9h1S4UYAMJmZS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9h1S4UYAMJmZS.jpeg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9h1S4UYAMJmZS-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9h1S4UYAMJmZS-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9h1S4UYAMJmZS-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9h1S4UYAMJmZS-1080x1440.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2.中共党和国家领导人的提法和禁忌（甚至还有“编辑失误案例”）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9nr1cUcAA2-y2.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624670\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9nr1cUcAA2-y2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9nr1cUcAA2-y2.jpeg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9nr1cUcAA2-y2-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9nr1cUcAA2-y2-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9nr1cUcAA2-y2-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9nr1cUcAA2-y2-1080x1440.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>3.重大政治提法和历史问题</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9oUkZVAAAoUHf.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624671\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9oUkZVAAAoUHf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9oUkZVAAAoUHf.jpeg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9oUkZVAAAoUHf-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9oUkZVAAAoUHf-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9oUkZVAAAoUHf-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9oUkZVAAAoUHf-1080x1440.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>4.民族和宗教问题</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rCUEAAyKMp.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624672\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rCUEAAyKMp.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rCUEAAyKMp.jpeg 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rCUEAAyKMp-225x300.jpeg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rJVUAAm1QG.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624673\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rJVUAAm1QG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rJVUAAm1QG.jpeg 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rJVUAAm1QG-225x300.jpeg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rNVAAIYeri.jpeg\"><br />\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624674\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rNVAAIYeri.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rNVAAIYeri.jpeg 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9o_rNVAAIYeri-225x300.jpeg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>5.港澳台和国际组织的一些禁忌</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9pbRuVUAATdwH.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624675\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9pbRuVUAATdwH.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9pbRuVUAATdwH.jpeg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9pbRuVUAATdwH-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9pbRuVUAATdwH-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9pbRuVUAATdwH-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9pbRuVUAATdwH-1080x1440.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>6.地图问题</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6UwAERm8T.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624676\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6UwAERm8T.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6UwAERm8T.jpeg 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6UwAERm8T-225x300.jpeg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6VAAAljKN.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624677\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6VAAAljKN.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6VAAAljKN.jpeg 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL9p4n6VAAAljKN-225x300.jpeg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>7.港澳台问题</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsaUYAEJK_Z.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-624678\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsaUYAEJK_Z.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsaUYAEJK_Z.jpeg 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsaUYAEJK_Z-81x300.jpeg 81w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsaUYAEJK_Z-413x1536.jpeg 413w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 551px) 100vw, 551px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsbU8AAhrWm.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-624679\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsbU8AAhrWm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsbU8AAhrWm.jpeg 548w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsbU8AAhrWm-80x300.jpeg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsbU8AAhrWm-274x1024.jpeg 274w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EL93CsbU8AAhrWm-411x1536.jpeg 411w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" /></a></p>\n<p>事实上，这类文件并非“高度机密”，例如2018年1月，某官方微信公众号 @中文编辑校对网 就曾将《涉及台港澳藏疆的词语正确用语》<strong>（1）</strong>的部分文件公开化。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"mLIPIkw2QN\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e6%b6%89%e5%8f%8a%e5%8f%b0%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e8%97%8f%e7%96%86%e7%9a%84%e8%af%8d%e8%af%ad-%e5%bf%85%e9%a1%bb%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8%e5%ae%98%e6%96%b9/\">【异闻观止】涉及台港澳藏疆的词语 必须使用官方统一口径</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【异闻观止】涉及台港澳藏疆的词语 必须使用官方统一口径》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e6%b6%89%e5%8f%8a%e5%8f%b0%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e8%97%8f%e7%96%86%e7%9a%84%e8%af%8d%e8%af%ad-%e5%bf%85%e9%a1%bb%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8%e5%ae%98%e6%96%b9/embed/#?secret=mLIPIkw2QN\" data-secret=\"mLIPIkw2QN\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>从这些媒体与出版社的统一报道规范要求中我们可以看到，一些涉港涉台用语的<strong>中立表述</strong>是被完全禁止的，例如中华民国、台湾总统、占领中环等，这使得中国媒体、书本用语被官方高度统一化、主观意识形态化，未经官方批准使用的“用语”即为高度危险的“敏感用语”，公开化使用后果严重。长此执行，中国民众也形成了严厉的自我审查机制，同官方审查相互配合。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"FoCkPZRTAU\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e6%97%b6%e6%8a%a5%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%8e%e8%94%a1%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%e6%8b%8d%e7%89%87%e9%81%ad%e4%b8%ad%e6%96%b9%e6%96%bd%e5%8e%8b%e6%b3%a2%e7%89%b9%e7%8e%8b%e6%8b%92%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4/\">自由时报｜与蔡英文拍片遭中方施压波特王拒删除影片</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《自由时报｜与蔡英文拍片遭中方施压波特王拒删除影片》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e6%97%b6%e6%8a%a5%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%8e%e8%94%a1%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%e6%8b%8d%e7%89%87%e9%81%ad%e4%b8%ad%e6%96%b9%e6%96%bd%e5%8e%8b%e6%b3%a2%e7%89%b9%e7%8e%8b%e6%8b%92%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4/embed/#?secret=FoCkPZRTAU\" data-secret=\"FoCkPZRTAU\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>一名前中国媒体从业人员告知CDT，这类文件“十几年前就是入职编辑人手一份”，这些“都有看过”，内容“感觉没有太大变化”。而最大的变化可能是，这些审查准则从“内部”推向到了“国际”。</p>\n","author":972,"categories":[18271,38895,38912,8649],"tags":[8639,18904,14205,32985,9249,39529,9038,28510,30398]}